0without%20providing%20you%20notice.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cbr%3ESources%20of%20Information%3C/h3%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20collect%20your%20Personal%20Information%20from%20the%20following%20sources:%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou.%3C/strong%3E%20We%20may%20collect%20Personal%20Information%20directly%20from%20you%20such%20as%20through%20your%20use%20of%20our%20website,%20facilities%20or%20systems,%20when%20you%20send%20us%20an%20email,%20contact%20us%20by%20phone,%20or%20otherwise%20communicate%20or%20interact%20with%20us.%20We%20may%20also%20collect%20information%20when%20you%20are%20an%20applicant%20for%20employment%20with%20us%20or%20employed%20by%20us.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelated%20Entities%20and%20Affiliates.%3C/strong%3E%20We%20may%20collect%20information%20about%20you%20from%20our%20related%20parties%20and%20affiliates.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20and%20related%20services.%3C/strong%3E%20We%20may%20collect%20information%20about%20you%20through%20your%20social%20media%20services%20consistent%20with%20your%20settings%20on%20such%20services.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%20parties.%3C/strong%3E%20We%20may%20collect%20information%20about%20you%20from%20third%20parties%20such%20as%20your%20references,%20background%20check%20vendors,%20staffing%20agencies,%20clients,%20or%20other%20third-party%20sources%20that%20are%20lawfully%20entitled%20to%20share%20your%20data%20with%20us.%20This%20may%20include%20service%20providers%20or%20contractors%20who%20collect%20or%20process%20your%20personal%20information%20on%20our%20behalf.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cbr%3EHow%20We%20Disclose%20Your%20Personal%20Information%3C/h3%3E%0A%3Cp%3ETo%20carry%20out%20the%20purposes%20outlined%20above,%20we%20may%20disclose%20your%20personal%20information%20to%20our%20affiliates,%20service%20providers%20and%20contractors,%20and%20government%20entities.%20We%20may%20also%20disclose%20your%20personal%20information%20to%20third%20parties,%20if%20necessary,%20to:%20(1)%20comply%20with%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20laws;%20(2)%20comply%20with%20a%20civil,%20criminal,%20or%20regulatory%20inquiry,%20investigation,%20subpoena,%20or%20summons%20by%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20authorities;%20(3)%20cooperate%20with%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20concerning%20conduct%20or%20activity%20that%20we%20reasonably%20and%20in%20good%20faith%20believe%20may%20violate%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20laws;%20or%20(4)%20exercise%20or%20defend%20legal%20claims.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3ELastly,%20we%20may%20transfer%20personal%20information%20to%20a%20third%20party%20as%20part%20of%20a%20merger,%20acquisition,%20bankruptcy,%20or%20other%20transaction%20in%20which%20the%20third%20party%20assumes%20control%20or%20acquires%20of%20all%20or%20part%20of%20the%20assets%20of%20our%20business.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20preceding%20twelve%20(12)%20months,%20we%20have%20disclosed%20the%20following%20categories%20of%20personal%20information%20for%20a%20business%20purpose:%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EIdentifiers%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EPersonal%20information%20categories%20listed%20in%20the%20California%20Customer%20Records%20statute%20(Cal.%20Civ.%20Code%20&amp;sect;%201798.80(e))%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EProtected%20classification%20characteristics%20under%20California%20or%20federal%20law%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EInternet%20or%20other%20similar%20network%20activity%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EGeolocation%20data%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3ESensory%20data%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EProfessional%20or%20employment-related%20information%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EInferences%20drawn%20from%20other%20personal%20information%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3ESensitive%20personal%20information%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20disclose%20your%20personal%20information%20for%20a%20business%20purpose%20to%20the%20following%20categories%20of%20third%20parties:%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EThird%20parties%20as%20directed%20by%20you.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EOur%20clients%20or%20customers.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20business%20partners.%3C/strong%3E%20For%20example,%20we%20might%20disclose%20your%20personal%20information%20to%20one%20of%20our%20business%20partners%20for%20purposes%20of%20collaborating%20on%20services%20or%20an%20event.%20Where%20applicable,%20we%20encourage%20you%20to%20review%20each%20such%20business%20partner&apos;s%20privacy%20statement%20before%20signing%20on%20with%20them.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EServices%20provider/contractors.%3C/strong%3E%20For%20example,%20we%20may%20disclose%20information%20to%20service%20providers%20that%20assist%20with%20payment%20processing,%20analyzing%20data,%20processing%20and%20fulfilling%20orders,%20background%20checks,%20marketing%20and%20advertising%20companies,%20information%20technology%20providers,%20and%20data%20storage%20companies.%20We%20might%20also%20authorize%20our%20service%20providers%20to%20collect%20personal%20information%20on%20our%20behalf.%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3EThird%20parties%20as%20necessary%20to%20comply%20with%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20laws;%20comply%20with%20a%20civil,%20criminal,%20or%20regulatory%20inquiry,%20investigation,%20subpoena,%20or%20summons%20by%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20authorities;%20cooperate%20with%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20concerning%20conduct%20or%20activity%20that%20we%20reasonably%20and%20in%20good%20faith%20believe%20may%20violate%20federal,%20state,%20or%20local%20laws;%20detect,%20investigate%20and%20prevent%20fraud%20or%20other%20unlawful%20activities;%20to%20protect%20and%20defend%20ourselves,%20our%20property,%20our%20employees,%20our%20customers,%20and%20our%20users;%20and%20to%20exercise%20or%20defend%20legal%20claims.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0A%3Cp%3EThe%20Company%20may%20add%20to%20the%20categories%20of%20Personal%20Information%20it%20collects%20and%20the%20purposes%20it%20uses%20Personal%20Information.%20In%20that%20case,%20the%20Company%20will%20inform%20you.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20sell%20or%20share,%20as%20those%20terms%20are%20defined%20by%20the%20CCPA,%20the%20above%20categories%20of%20Personal%20Information.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20use%20or%20disclose%20your%20Sensitive%20Personal%20Information%20for%20purposes%20that,%20with%20limited%20exceptions,%20are%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20application%20or%20employment%20related%20purpose%20for%20which%20we%20collect%20it%20or%20as%20reasonably%20expected%20by%20an%20average%20individual%20in%20this%20context%20or%20for%20other%20permitted%20purposes%20under%20the%20CCPA%20or%20as%20authorized%20by%20regulation.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cbr%3ERetention%3C/h3%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20retain%20your%20Personal%20Information%20for%20as%20long%20as%20is%20necessary%20to%20satisfy%20the%20purpose%20for%20which%20we%20collect%20it%20such%20as%20processing%20your%20application%20for%20employment,%20managing%20the%20employment%20relationship,%20etc.%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Company&apos;s%20data%20retention%20schedule.%20We%20may%20retain%20your%20Personal%20Information%20for%20longer%20if%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20comply%20with%20our%20legal%20or%20reporting%20obligations%20(for%20example,%20if%20we%20are%20required%20to%20retain%20your%20data%20to%20comply%20with%20applicable%20laws),%20resolve%20disputes,%20enforce%20our%20legal%20agreements%20and%20policies,%20address%20other%20legitimate%20business%20needs,%20or%20as%20permitted%20or%20required%20by%20applicable%20law.%20We%20may%20also%20retain%20your%20Personal%20Information%20in%20a%20deidentified%20or%20aggregated%20form%20so%20that%20it%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20associated%20with%20you.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20appropriate%20retention%20period%20for%20your%20Personal%20Information,%20we%20consider%20various%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20amount,%20nature,%20and%20sensitivity%20of%20your%20information;%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20unauthorized%20access,%20use%20or%20disclosure;%20the%20purposes%20for%20which%20we%20collect%20or%20process%20your%20personal%20information;%20and%20applicable%20legal%20requirements.%20Personal%20information%20does%20not%20include%20certain%20categories%20of%20information,%20such%20as%20publicly%20available%20information%20from%20government%20records,%20and%20deidentified%20or%20aggregated%20consumer%20information.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20required%20to%20maintain%20records%20of%20Consumer%20requests%20submitted%20under%20California%20Privacy%20Laws,%20which%20may%20include%20this%20category%20of%20Personal%20Information,%20and%20how%20we%20responded%20to%20such%20requests%20for%20at%20least%20twenty-four%20(24)%20months.%20Such%20information%20related%20to%20Consumer%20requests%20is%20retained%20only%20for%20recordkeeping%20purposes.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch3%3E%3Cbr%3ECalifornia%20Resident%20Individual%20Rights%20Requests%3C/h3%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20who%20are%20residents%20of%20the%20State%20of%20California%20have%20certain%20individual%20rights,%20which%20are%20outlined%20below.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ERight%20To%20Know%20About%20Personal%20Information%20Collected%20or%20Disclosed%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20California%20resident,%20you%20have%20the%20right%20to%20request%20additional%20information,%20beyond%20that%20disclosed%20above,%20regarding%20the%20following,%20to%20the%20extent%20applicable:%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20categories%20of%20Personal%20Information%20the%20Company%20collected%20about%20you%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20categories%20of%20sources%20from%20which%20that%20Personal%20Information%20was%20collected%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20business%20or%20commercial%20purposes%20for%20which%20that%20information%20was%20collected,%20sold,%20or%20shared%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20categories%20of%20third%20parties%20to%20whom%20the%20information%20was%20disclosed%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20specific%20pieces%20of%20Personal%20Information%20collected%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0A%3Cp%3EUpon%20receipt%20of%20a%20verifiable%20request%20to%20know%20(see%20below),%20and%20as%20required%20by%20applicable%20law,%20we%20will%20provide%20a%20response%20to%20such%20request.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ERight%20To%20Request%20Deletion%20of%20Your%20Personal%20Information%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20request%20that%20we%20delete%20the%20Personal%20Information%20we%20collected%20or%20maintain%20about%20you.%20Once%20we%20receive%20your%20request,%20we%20will%20let%20you%20know%20what,%20if%20any,%20Personal%20Information%20we%20can%20delete%20from%20our%20records,%20and%20will%20direct%20any%20service%20providers,%20contractors%20and%20third%20parties%20to%20whom%20we%20disclosed%20your%20Personal%20Information%20to%20also%20delete%20your%20Personal%20Information%20from%20their%20records.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20be%20circumstances%20where%20we%20cannot%20delete%20your%20Personal%20Information%20or%20direct%20service%20providers%20or%20contractors%20to%20delete%20your%20Personal%20Information%20from%20their%20records.%20Such%20instances%20include,%20without%20limitation,%20when%20the%20information%20at%20issue%20is%20maintained:%20(a)%20to%20enable%20solely%20internal%20uses%20that%20are%20reasonably%20aligned%20with%20your%20expectations%20based%20on%20your%20relationship%20with%20the%20Company%20and%20compatible%20with%20the%20context%20in%20which%20you%20provided%20the%20information,%20or%20(b)%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20legal%20obligation.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EUpon%20receipt%20of%20a%20verifiable%20request%20to%20delete%20(see%20below),%20and%20as%20required%20by%20applicable%20law,%20we%20will%20provide%20a%20response%20to%20such%20requests.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ERight%20to%20Request%20Correction%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20request%20that%20the%20Company%20correct%20any%20inaccurate%20Personal%20Information%20we%20maintain%20about%20you,%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20nature%20of%20that%20information%20and%20purpose%20for%20processing%20it.%20Upon%20receipt%20of%20a%20verifiable%20request%20to%20correct%20(see%20below),%20and%20as%20required%20by%20the%20CCPA,%20we%20will%20provide%20a%20response%20to%20such%20requests.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ERight%20to%20Non-Discrimination%20for%20the%20Exercise%20of%20Your%20Privacy%20Rights%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20not%20discriminate%20or%20retaliate%20against%20you%20for%20exercising%20any%20of%20the%20rights%20described%20above.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ESubmitting%20CCPA%20Rights%20Requests%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3ETo%20submit%20a%20CCPA%20Rights%20request%20as%20outlined%20above,%20please%20contact%20the%20Company&apos;s%20Compliance%20Department%20by%20calling%20us%20at%20(800)%20893-9698%20ext.1225%20or%20emailing%20us%20at%20%3Ca%20href=%22mailto:privacy_officer@scp-health.com%22%3Eprivacy_officer@scp-health.com%3C/a%3E.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20reserve%20the%20right%20to%20only%20respond%20to%20verifiable%20consumer%20requests%20to%20know,%20delete,%20or%20correct%20that%20are%20submitted%20as%20instructed.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EA%20verifiable%20consumer%20request%20is%20one%20made%20by%20any%20individual%20who%20is:%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20individual%20who%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20request,%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ean%20individual%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20individual&apos;s%20minor%20child,%20or%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3Ethe%20authorized%20agent%20of%20the%20individual.%3C/li%3E%0A%3C/ul%3E%0A%3Ch4%3EWhat%20to%20submit%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20request,%20you%20must%20provide%20us%20with%20sufficient%20information%20to%20verify%20your%20identity%20and/or%20authority%20to%20act%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20individual.%20In%20general,%20we%20may%20ask%20you%20to%20provide%20identifying%20information%20that%20we%20already%20maintain%20about%20you%20or%20we%20may%20use%20a%20third-party%20verification%20service.%20In%20either%20event,%20we%20will%20try%20to%20avoid%20asking%20you%20for%20sensitive%20Personal%20Information%20to%20verify%20your%20identity.%20We%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20your%20request%20or%20provide%20you%20with%20Personal%20Information%20if%20we%20cannot%20verify%20your%20identity%20or%20authority%20to%20make%20the%20request%20and%20confirm%20the%20Personal%20Information%20relates%20to%20you.%20However,%20making%20a%20verifiable%20request%20does%20not%20require%20you%20to%20create%20an%20account%20with%20us.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3EAdditionally,%20you%20will%20need%20to%20describe%20your%20request%20with%20sufficient%20detail%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20review,%20understand,%20assess,%20and%20respond.%20We%20will%20not%20use%20the%20Personal%20Information%20we%20collect%20from%20an%20individual%20to%20determine%20a%20verifiable%20request%20for%20any%20other%20purpose,%20except%20as%20required%20or%20permitted%20by%20law.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3EAuthorized%20Agent%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20authorize%20a%20natural%20person%20or%20a%20business%20(the%20Agent)%20to%20act%20on%20your%20behalf.%20When%20you%20submit%20a%20Request%20to%20Know,%20Correct,%20or%20Delete,%20the%20Agent%20must%20provide%20proof%20that%20you%20gave%20the%20Agent%20signed%20permission%20to%20submit%20the%20request,%20and%20you%20either%20must%20(i)%20verify%20you%20own%20identity%20with%20the%20business%20or%20(ii)%20directly%20confirm%20with%20us%20that%20you%20provide%20permission%20to%20the%20Agent.%20However,%20these%20steps%20are%20not%20required%20when%20you%20have%20provided%20the%20authorized%20agent%20with%20power%20of%20attorney%20pursuant%20to%20Probate%20Code%20sections%204000%20to%204465.%20We%20reserve%20the%20right%20to%20deny%20requests%20from%20persons%20or%20businesses%20claiming%20to%20be%20authorized%20agents%20that%20do%20not%20submit%20sufficient%20proof%20of%20their%20authorization.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3ESpouses,%20Dependents,%20and%20Associates%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20knowledge%20that%20the%20Company%20collected%20Personal%20Information%20related%20to%20your%20spouse,%20dependent,%20or%20associate,%20please%20share%20a%20copy%20of%20this%20notice%20with%20all%20such%20individuals.%3C/p%3E%0A%3Ch4%3E%3Cbr%3EUpdates%3C/h4%3E%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20reserve%20the%20right%20to%20amend%20this%20notice%20at%20any%20time%20without%20advance%20notice.%20Please%20direct%20questions%20about%20this%20notice%20to%20%3Ca%20href=%22mailto:privacy_officer@scp-health.com%22%3Eprivacy_officer@scp-health.com%3C/a%3E.%3C/p%3E&quot;,&quot;card&quot;:&quot;{card}&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;styleObject&quot;:{&quot;sizeClass&quot;:&quot;slds-size_12-of-12&quot;},&quot;elementLabel&quot;:&quot;Block-8-Text-0&quot;,&quot;key&quot;:&quot;element_element_block_0_0_outputField_0_0&quot;,&quot;parentElementKey&quot;:&quot;element_block_0_0&quot;}],&quot;elementLabel&quot;:&quot;Block-8&quot;}]}},&quot;childCards&quot;:[],&quot;actions&quot;:[],&quot;omniscripts&quot;:[],&quot;documents&quot;:[]}],&quot;dataSource&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;value&quot;:{},&quot;orderBy&quot;:{},&quot;contextVariables&quot;:[]},&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Competency_CCPA_Notice_Description&quot;,&quot;enableLwc&quot;:true,&quot;isFlex&quot;:true,&quot;theme&quot;:&quot;slds&quot;,&quot;selectableMode&quot;:&quot;Multi&quot;,&quot;xmlObject&quot;:{&quot;masterLabel&quot;:&quot;Competency_CCPA_Notice_Description&quot;,&quot;isExposed&quot;:true,&quot;apiVersion&quot;:56}}</propertySetConfig>
